records.short_description: RPA ORX SPH COGNITIVE MRD HOLD RELEASE - IRIS Screens are stucked due to which orders are not picked up by bots
records.close_notes:
Issue: RPA ORX SPH COGNITIVE MRD HOLD RELEASE - IRIS Screens are stucked due to which orders are not picked up by bots
Impact: High
RCA: Orders are being stuck In progress and not able to process the inventories for RPA ORX SPH COGNITIVE MRD HOLD RELEASE when bot is applying the manual hold and connecting with hive started, getting stuck and not able to process the order for a longer period of time which in turn is impacting the AHT of the automation.

As of now the issue is resolved and the BOTs have started to process the inventory.
The BOT was stuck due to HIVE table getting locked and not allowing the BOT to continue forward post processing the order.

Conclusion: We are closing the INC as of now as the Automation is working fine and the orders are getting processed by the BOT
